{
  "texts": [
    "Their experiments also demonstrate that the trained attacker exhibits good transferability to unseen instructions.",
    "Building on the aforementioned insights, we propose JUMP, a jailbreak framework designed to optimize universal multi-prompts.",
    "By utilizing an additional model as an attacker, we generate adversarial suffixes through a beam search process.",
    "The key contributions of our work are as follows:",
    "• Our method, JUMP, is an extended version of BEAST, focusing on a more general scenario without the need for training models."
  ]
}